-[violet chuckles]

03:03.067 --> 03:05.267
taking self-care
to a whole new level.

03:05.352 --> 03:11.573
Yeah, I'm just saving
my energy for ralph angel
and darla's baby shower.

03:11.659 --> 03:15.861
You know, I know everybody's
dealing with their own battles
right now, but...

03:15.946 --> 03:18.614
We still need to make time
to rejoice, right?

03:18.699 --> 03:19.781
I know that's right.

03:21.285 --> 03:23.985
But, look here, baby.
I'mma let you chill out.
You just holler at me,

03:24.088 --> 03:25.754
-if you need anything,
all right?
-Mmm-hmm.

03:25.839 --> 03:26.755
[cell phone vibrating]

03:29.343 --> 03:30.459
[laughing]

03:31.679 --> 03:33.462
what are you laughing at?

03:33.547 --> 03:36.014
