it ain't gabe's fault, right?

04:10.718 --> 04:12.701
Hi, there.
Delivery for darla bordelon?

04:12.803 --> 04:15.053
Right on time.
Perfect, thank you.

04:15.139 --> 04:19.741
Um, let's get
that big arrangement there.

04:19.843 --> 04:25.430
And the two smaller ones,
we'll have over at that table.
Thank you, so much.

04:25.516 --> 04:28.967
Looks terrific.
Uh, let's get some succulents
near the stairs, please.

04:29.069 --> 04:29.818
Just to brighten it up.

04:29.937 --> 04:31.353
-I'll take care of it.
-Thank you.

04:32.489 --> 04:35.490
Hey, hey, hey.
Save some
for our guests, will ya?

04:35.592 --> 04:38.827
It's a baby shower.
Not the xavier cafeteria.

04:38.929 --> 04:41.463
I wish xavier
had mangoes this ripe.

04:41.565 --> 04:43.398
[chuckles] had these flown in.

04:43.500 --> 04:45.817
Darla's been addicted
to these the last couple
of months.

04:45.903 --> 04:47.436
