-micah!

04:53.010 --> 04:55.761
I'm sorry, last one,
last one, I promise.

04:55.846 --> 04:57.629
-Saving the rest for darla.
-Heh.

04:59.266 --> 05:03.051
Can you believe
we're gonna have a little one
in the family again?

05:05.556 --> 05:06.772
I remember
when you were that small.

05:08.309 --> 05:12.227
It is amazing to me,
sometimes when I look
at you now.

05:12.313 --> 05:13.562
I can't imagine
what that's like.

05:14.982 --> 05:17.482
It's surreal
and strange sometimes.

05:19.286 --> 05:25.907
But most of the time,
it's, uh, it's perfectly
natural and almost expected.

05:25.993 --> 05:29.961
I mean...
You're everything
I dreamed you'd be.

05:30.047 --> 05:31.413
Aw, thank you, ma.

05:32.666 --> 05:35.334
-[both laugh]
-that really means a lot
coming from you.

05:37.171 --> 05:38.170
Hmm.

05:39.957 --> 05:40.956
-You okay, baby?
-Yeah.

05:41.925 --> 05:45.543
And, hey,
I'm really proud of you.

05:45.646 --> 05:47.679
You're on the road
with the party one day.

05:47.765 --> 05:49.431
Throwing a party
for the family the next.

05:50.567 --> 05:53.852
-You really are wonder woman.
-Mmm, thank you.

05:53.937 --> 05:58.106
Oh, ah, the balloons
go on the back deck there.
Thank you.

05:58.192 --> 06:01.159
