be a little too big
for the table.

06:03.864 --> 06:06.164
So why don't we put these
in the back patio

06:06.250 --> 06:10.068
and have some smaller
arrangements for the tables.

06:10.170 --> 06:11.703
I mean, to sort of, you know,
brighten it up.

06:13.707 --> 06:15.540
