are old enough to free ernest
from the suspicion of murder.

08:05.736 --> 08:07.486
-Right.
-But...

08:08.822 --> 08:11.206
The data revealed
two new details.

08:11.308 --> 08:14.910
One, that the bones
are from late 1800s.

08:16.497 --> 08:21.750
And second...
[sighs] that the remains
are from multiple people.

08:21.835 --> 08:24.419
-As in...
-As in a community, nova.

08:24.505 --> 08:25.921
We think
it's a larger graveyard.

08:27.341 --> 08:28.423
Oh.

08:34.665 --> 08:35.830
[sighs]

08:37.584 --> 08:39.034
oh, god. I don't...

08:46.210 --> 08:49.244
[prosper] ah, what a sight
for sore eyes you are.

08:49.346 --> 08:53.064
Like your mother,
spitting image
and just as beautiful.

08:54.601 --> 08:57.269
Thank you, daddy.
I needed that.

08:57.371 --> 09:02.524
No, no, you already
got everything you need
right here and right here

09:02.609 --> 09:04.276
-and me by your side.
-[both laugh]

09:04.394 --> 09:05.193
I know that.

09:07.231 --> 09:11.950
[sighs] now I've made
my mistakes,
but now that I'm here,

09:12.069 --> 09:13.368
I'm staying here.

09:17.574 --> 09:20.742
I don't know, I...
Just hope they accept me.

09:22.746 --> 09:26.798
'cause a lot has happened
and a lot has been said.

09:26.917 --> 09:28.550
Yeah, well,
things that need to be said,

09:28.635 --> 09:30.252
but you weren't wrong
about any of them.

09:31.471 --> 09:35.473
Just know that you're loved.
And not just by me.

09:37.844 --> 09:40.228
[sighs] we're gonna
have a good one today, okay?

09:40.314 --> 09:43.098
-[billie] okay.
-All right, we got this.

09:48.939 --> 09:50.638
-Oh, yeah, we got this.
-[prosper laughs]

09:50.741 --> 09:51.606
[both laughing]

09:55.762 --> 09:58.830
[ralph angel] all right.
Mmm-hmm.

