to the national museum
of african american history.

10:46.163 --> 10:47.629
And we went to...

10:49.833 --> 10:51.950
What are those boxes for?

10:52.052 --> 10:55.220
We can talk about that later.
After the shower, okay?

10:56.056 --> 10:56.871
All right.

10:57.724 --> 11:00.058
Actually, blue, what you say
we, uh...

11:01.528 --> 11:02.594
Take us a little walk.

11:05.265 --> 11:06.348
Want to talk to you.

11:09.269 --> 11:10.101
Okay.

11:17.527 --> 11:18.360
[door opening]

11:21.198 --> 11:22.163
[door closing]

11:25.702 --> 11:29.020
I mean, the way they started,
and all they been through,

11:29.122 --> 11:31.256
just proves that love
makes all things possible.

11:31.375 --> 11:34.342
Well,
they are a strong couple.

11:34.428 --> 11:38.380
So she kicked her addiction
and now he's single-handedly
running the farm.

11:38.465 --> 11:41.132
I mean,
those are major turn arounds.

11:41.218 --> 11:45.420
They are.
They still have challenges,
but more triumphs.

11:45.522 --> 11:47.305
I'm hoping that some
of the information
that you uncovered

11:47.391 --> 11:50.258
about the bones on the farm
may lead somewhere.

11:50.360 --> 11:52.694
I can't just let that land
be handed over to the landrys.

11:53.647 --> 11:56.147
I'm not giving up.
None of us are.

11:57.617 --> 12:00.402
Always keep fighting.
That's the motto.

12:00.487 --> 12:04.105
Yeah,
but we gotta celebrate, too.

12:04.207 --> 12:07.575
[laughs] they deserve this
today and charley's pulling
out all the stops at her place

12:07.661 --> 12:09.077
and it should
be really lovely.

12:09.162 --> 12:10.228
Well, you look gorgeous.

12:12.249 --> 12:13.581
I do?

12:13.667 --> 12:15.133
I'll happily say it again.

12:17.254 --> 12:18.253
You look gorgeous.

12:22.542 --> 12:23.842
Call me when you get back.

12:23.927 --> 12:25.593
-Can you bring me a vi's pie?
-Uh, really?

12:25.679 --> 12:27.979
Please, any slice,
I'll take it.

12:28.098 --> 12:29.431
Wanna come get some yourself?

12:31.435 --> 12:35.153
I... Yeah. Yeah, I would.

12:37.908 --> 12:39.407
Good. Okay.

12:44.014 --> 12:45.730
-[hollywood] hey.
-Hi.

12:45.849 --> 12:46.848
[violet laughs]

12:46.933 --> 12:48.216
