not to bake or cook,

12:57.194 --> 13:00.728
but, uh, I had to make
my baby boy blue's
favorite pie.

13:00.831 --> 13:02.197
Pies, I see.

13:02.282 --> 13:04.532
Yeah, well, you know,
he likes everything she makes,

13:04.618 --> 13:07.335
-so she went ahead
and made everything.
-[micah and charley laugh]

13:08.205 --> 13:09.704
he has not been here
for a long time

13:09.790 --> 13:11.790
and he should not
have to choose.

13:11.875 --> 13:15.593
You know what?
You are very right,
he should not.

13:15.695 --> 13:17.011
-Lord.
-Oh!

13:17.097 --> 13:18.713
-[violet laughs]
-oh!

13:18.799 --> 13:22.383
