Doesn't she?
-She certainly does, yeah.

13:29.109 --> 13:30.758
That girl has gone
through a lot.

13:30.861 --> 13:33.278
We should make this day
extra special for her.

13:34.231 --> 13:36.314
-And ralph angel.
-[chuckles] true.

13:36.399 --> 13:37.982
[charley and hollywood laugh]

13:38.068 --> 13:40.401
-[hollywood] let me see
about that champagne.
-[hollywood and violet laugh]

13:43.690 --> 13:45.890
