we was at the playground?
We had the churros?

14:17.407 --> 14:19.157
Me, you and kenya?

14:19.259 --> 14:21.109
-[ralph angel] yeah.
-I remember.

14:21.194 --> 14:22.427
[ralph angel chuckles]

14:22.529 --> 14:25.897
-there was a basketball game.
-[ralph angel] that's right.

14:27.868 --> 14:31.035
